{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "第十三回 无妄之灾\n\n李寻欢与林诗音在李园对峙，林诗音质问李寻欢为何回来扰乱她平静的生活，李寻欢黯然离去，独坐荷塘石阶。他前往冷香小筑寻找林仙儿，发现屋内人去楼空，五只酒杯嵌入桌面形成梅花图案，疑为梅花盗所为。此时田七、赵正义、公孙摩云等群豪包围冷香小筑，诬指李寻欢为梅花盗。龙啸云试图为李寻欢辩解，却被赵正义以义结金兰为由压制。田七三人围住李寻欢，却因忌惮小李飞刀不敢先出手。龙啸云假意揽住李寻欢肩头，实则配合田七出手，李寻欢被金丝夹翅软棍击中腿部，又被公孙摩云点了七处大穴，赵正义踢其滚出两丈。李寻欢虽身陷囹圄仍傲骨不屈，面对赵正义的折磨微笑以对。阿飞突然出现，一拳击退公孙摩云，并带来真正的梅花盗尸体。林仙儿揭示梅花盗杀人秘密：利用腹语术用腹部说话，嘴里藏暗器钢筒，在对话时突然射出暗器。阿飞与田七等人对峙，证明李寻欢并非梅花盗。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "不错，我是个无可救药的浪子，我若去找她，就是害了她……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你答应了我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你难道不知道我一向都很喜欢害人么？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "告辞了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你既已走了，为什么又要回来？我们本来生活得很平静，你……你为什么又要来扰乱我们？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你害了我的孩子还不够？还要去害她？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "其实你根本用不着求我的，因为我根本就没有看上过她！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我既已走了，为什么还要回来……为什么还要回来……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道我看错了！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "林姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "梅花盗，你已逃不了，快出来送死吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算你有通天的本事，我们今日也叫你死无葬身之地！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老实告诉你，洛阳府的田七爷今天已赶来了，还有'摩云手'公孙大侠，再加上赵大爷，龙四爷……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫要乱，先静下来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友既已到了这里，为何不肯出来相见？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位既已到了这里，为何不肯进来相见？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子是想诱我们入屋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敌暗我明，咱们可千万不能上他的当！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_mo_yun",
      "speaker_name": "公孙摩云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "梅花盗本来就是只会在暗中偷鸡狗之辈，哪里敢见人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "偷鸡摸狗，缩头乌龟，不敢见人，如何如何……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，梅花盗确是有些鬼鬼祟祟，但和我又有何关系？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_mo_yun",
      "speaker_name": "公孙摩云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你不是梅花盗是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_mo_yun",
      "text": "公孙大侠还问他干什么，赵大爷绝不会看错的，此人必是梅花盗无疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "赵正义，我早就知道这都是你玩的花样！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位莫动手，这是我的兄弟，李寻欢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "赵大爷你高明的眼力，若非在下手脚还算灵便，此刻已做了梅花盗的替死鬼了，那死得才叫冤枉。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "三更半夜，一个人鬼鬼祟祟地躲在这里，我不将他看成梅花盗将他看成谁？我怎知阁下的病忽然好了，又偷偷溜到这里来？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "我用不着偷偷溜到这里来，无论哪里，我都可光明正大地走来走去，何况，赵大爷又怎知不是此间的主人约我来的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我倒不知道阁下和林姑娘有这份交情，只不过，谁都知道林姑娘今夜是绝不会到这里来的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "林姑娘为了躲避梅花盗，今天下午已搬出了冷香小筑。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "纵然如此，阁下先问清楚了再下毒手也不迟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "对付梅花盗这种人，只有先下手为强，等问清楚再出手，就已迟了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "好个先下手为强！如此说来，李某今日若死在赵大爷手上，也只能算我活该，一点也怨不得赵大爷。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "黑夜之间，无论谁都会偶然看错的，何况……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "何况，也许我并没有看错呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "没有看错？难道赵大爷认为李某就是梅花盗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那也难说得很，大家只知道梅花盗轻功很高，出手很快，至于他究竟是姓张，还是姓李，就谁也不知道了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "不错，李某轻功既不低，出手也不慢，梅花盗重现江湖，也正是李某再度入关的时候，李寻欢若不是梅花盗，那才是怪事一件。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "但赵大爷既然认定了李某就是梅花盗，此刻为何还不出手？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "早些出手，迟些出手都无妨，有田七爷和摩云兄在这里，今日你还想走得了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家只不过是在开玩笑，千万不可认真，龙啸云敢以身世性命担保，李寻欢绝不是梅花盗！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "这种事自然万万开不得玩笑的，你和他已有十年不见，怎能保证他？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "可是……可是我深知他的为人……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_mo_yun",
      "speaker_name": "公孙摩云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "知人知面不知心，这句话龙四爷总该听说过吧。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我田七和李探花也是数十年的交情了，但现在既然发生了这种事，我也只好将交情搁在一边。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "我朋友虽不少，但像田七爷这么样有身份的朋友我却一个也没有，田七爷也用不着跟我攀交情。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道三位此刻都恨不得立刻将我置之于死地，只因杀了我这梅花盗之后，非但立刻荣华富贵，美人在抱，而且还可换得个留芳百世的美名。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "黄金美人，等闲事耳，我们杀你，只不过是为了要替江湖除害而已。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "好光明呀，好堂皇，果然不愧为铁面无私，侠义无双！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "但阁下为何还不出手呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "哦，我知道了，田七爷'一条棍棒压天下，三颗铁胆镇乾坤'，赵大爷想必是在等着田七爷出手，田七爷自然也是义不容辞的了，是么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_mo_yun",
      "text": "田七爷难道也在等着公孙先生出手？嗯，不错，公孙先生'摩云十四式'矢矫变化，海内无双，自然是应该让公孙先生先出手的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒怪了，三位都想将我杀之而后快，却又都不肯出手，莫非三位都不愿抢先争功，在互相客气？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "兄弟，你到现在难道还看不出他们三位只不过是在跟你开玩笑？走走走，我们还是喝杯酒去挡挡寒气吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "大哥你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们怎能如此出手？！快放了他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "纵虎容易擒虎难，放不得的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "龙四爷，得罪了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "赵大哥，你……你怎能如此……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你我虽然义结金兰，但江湖道义却远重于兄弟之情，但愿你也能明白这道理，莫要再为这武林败类自讨苦吃了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "但他绝不是梅花盗，绝不是！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你还要多嘴？你怎能证明他不是梅花盗？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "连他自己都承认了，龙四爷又何苦再为他辩白？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_mo_yun",
      "speaker_name": "公孙摩云",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "龙四爷，你是有家有室，有身份，有地位的人，若是被这种淫棍拖累，岂非太不值得了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要你们先放了他，无论多大的罪，龙啸云都宁愿替他承当。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你愿为他承当？可是你的妻子呢？你的儿女呢？你难道也忍心眼看他们被你连累？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "兄弟，全是我害了你，我对不起你，对不起你……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "田七爷果然了不起，你看他那一棍出手有多快，就算龙四爷不在那里挡着，我看李寻欢也躲不开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何况旁边还有公孙大侠和赵大爷呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，难怪别人说赵大爷的两条腿可值万两黄金，你瞧他踢出去的那一腿，要多漂亮就有多漂亮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "常言道，南拳北腿，咱们北方的豪杰，腿法本就高强。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但公孙大侠的掌法又何尝弱了？若非他及时出手，李寻欢就算挨了一棍子，也未必会倒下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "田七爷，赵大爷，再加上公孙大侠，嘿，李寻欢今日撞着他们三位，真是倒了霉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "话虽是这么说，但若非龙四爷……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙四爷又怎样？他对李寻欢还不够义气吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙四爷可真是义气干云，李寻欢能交到他这种朋友，真是运气！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "兄弟，全是我该死，你交到我这朋友，实在是……是你的不幸，你……你这一生全是被我拖累的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "大哥，我只想要你明白一件事，若让我这一生重头再活一次，我还是会毫不考虑就交你这朋友的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "可是……若非我阻住了你出手，你又怎会……怎会……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我知道大哥你无论做什么，都是为了我好，我只有感激。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你为什么不告诉他们，你不是梅花盗！你为什么……为什么要……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "生死等闲事耳，我这一生本已活够了，生有何欢？死有何惧？为什么还要在这些匹夫小人面前卑躬曲膝！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "骂得好，骂得好！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_mo_yun",
      "speaker_name": "公孙摩云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他明白今日无论说什么，我们都不会放过他，也只好学那泼妇骂街，临死也落得个嘴上爽快了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，事已至此，我但求一死而已，但此刻李某掌中已无飞刀，各位为何还是不肯出手呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我们若是此刻就杀了你，江湖中难免会有你这样的不肖之徒，要说我们是假公济私，我们要杀你，也要杀得公公道道。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "赵正义，我真佩服你，你虽然满肚子男盗女娼，但说起话来却是句句仁义道德，而且居然一点也不脸红。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，姓李的，算你有胆子，你若想快点死，我倒有个法子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "我本来也想骂你几句，只不过却怕骂脏了我的嘴。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你若肯写张悔罪书，招供你的罪行，我们现在就让你舒舒服服地一死，你也算求仁得仁，死得不冤了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "好，我说，你写……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "兄弟，你招不得！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的罪孽实是四曲难数，罄笔难书，我假冒伪善，内心奸诈，夹私陷构，挑拨离间，趁入不备，偷施暗算，不仁不义，卑鄙无耻的事我几乎全都做尽了，但却还是大模大样地自命不凡！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "士可杀不可辱，你们不能如此折磨他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "text": "无妨，他打我一巴掌，我只当被疯狗咬了一口而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "姓李的，你听着，就算我还不愿杀你，但我却有本事让你求生不得，求死不能，你信不信？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若怕了你们这些卑鄙无耻，假仁假义的小人，我也枉为男子汉了！你们有什么手段，只管使出来吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zheng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "赵正义",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙啸云",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "兄弟，原谅我，你是英雄，但我……我却是个懦夫，我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "这怨不得大哥你，我若也有妻有子，也会和大哥同样做法的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "林姑娘，你是从哪里回来的？……这位是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_mo_yun",
      "speaker_name": "公孙摩云",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你是谁？想干什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_mo_yun",
      "text": "你是谁？你想干什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_mo_yun",
      "speaker_name": "公孙摩云",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我想教训教训你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他是你的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你看我会不会有这种朋友？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "朋友好快的出手，当真是长江后浪推前浪，江湖英雄出少年。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "在下田七，不知阁下高姓大名，可愿和田七交个朋友。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "我没有名字，也不愿交你这种朋友。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "少年人倒真是快人快语，只可惜交的朋友却选错了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他是你的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你可知道他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你也知道他就是梅花盗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "梅花盗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "这件事说来的确令人难以相信，只不过事实俱在，谁也无法否认。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "阁下若不信，不妨问问他自己……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "我不必问他，他绝不是梅花盗！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为这才是梅花盗！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你说这死人才是真正的梅花盗！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你毕竟太年轻，以为别人也和你同样容易上当，若是大家都去弄个死人回来，就说他是梅花盗，那岂非天下大乱了么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "我从来不骗人，也从来不会上当！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "那么，你怎能证明这死人是梅花盗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "你看看他的嘴！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我为何要看他的嘴，难道他的嘴还会动还会说话？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道他说得不错，这死人的确就是梅花盗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哦？难道是这死人自己告诉你的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "不错，的确是他自己告诉我的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秦重死的时候，我已看出他是中了一种很恶毒的暗器，但秦重躲不开这种暗器犹有可说，为何连吴问天那样的高人也躲不开这种暗器呢？我一直想不通这道理，因为这就是梅花盗的秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你现在难道已想通了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "不错，梅花盗的秘密就在他嘴里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因他跟别人说话的时候，暗器忽然自他嘴里射出来，所以别人根本没有警觉，也就无法闪避！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他嘴里咬着暗器钢筒，又怎能再和别人说话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "这就是他秘密中的秘密！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他并不用嘴说话，却用肚子来说话，他的嘴是用来杀人的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "田七爷在和人动手之前，眼睛会瞧在什么地方呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "自然是瞧在对方身上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "身上什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他的肩头和他的手！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就对了，高手相争，谁也不会瞪住对方的嘴，只有两条狗打架时，才会瞪住对方的嘴，因为人不像狗，绝不会用嘴咬人。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但梅花盗却偏偏是用嘴来杀人的，就因为谁也想不到世上会有这种事，所以才会被他暗算……越是高手，越容易被他暗算，因为高手对敌，眼睛绝不会瞧到对方肩头以上。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这秘密你怎会知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "我也是等他暗器发出之后才知道……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "那么，这位少年朋友难道是狗，一直在瞪着他的嘴么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 662
    }
  ],
